==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forefeel
<hw>Fore*feel"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To feel
beforehand; to have a presentiment of.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As when, with unwieldy waves, the great sea <qex>forefeels</qex>
winds.</q> <rj><qau>Chapman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forefence</ent>⟦br⟧
